The application:
===============

Rel 0
1. Provide a library that accesses the Strava API v2
2. Make it return POJO's, or use an HTTP REST API to return JSON
3. Make it optionally fall back to the Strava API v1?

Rel 1
1. Some rudimentary UI (in a second project) on the browser

Rel 2
4. Make it persist stuff to a graph DB for search
5. Make it do analytics


The technology:
==============
Some JAX-RS client or other
Jackson or similar to serialise/deserialise POJO
